    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and it\u2019s honestly been such a joy to own. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been well-loved and maintained throughout the years. It drives super smooth and is totally ready to hit the road for some new adventures! If you're looking for a dependable car that still looks great and runs beautifully, you\u2019ve found it. Feel free to reach out if you have any questions\u2014I'd love to see it go to a great home!",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
